    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "一、选择题",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            84,
            155,
            183,
            173
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（1）【答案】 (D).",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            179,
            252,
            194
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 由 $\\lim_{x\\to 0}f(x) = \\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{\\mathrm{e}^x - 1}{x} = 1 = f(0)$ 得 $f(x)$ 在 $x = 0$ 处连续；",
        "bbox": [
            115,
            201,
            767,
            233
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "再由 $\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{f(x) - f(0)}{x} = \\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{\\frac{\\mathrm{e}^x - 1}{x} - 1}{x} = \\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{\\mathrm{e}^x - 1 - x}{x^2} = \\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{\\mathrm{e}^x - 1}{2x} = \\frac{1}{2}$ 得",
        "bbox": [
            117,
            240,
            824,
            294
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$f^{\\prime}(0) = \\frac{1}{2}\\neq 0$ ，应选(D).",
        "bbox": [
            117,
            301,
            349,
            332
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（2）【答案】 (C).",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            340,
            248,
            356
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $f(x + 1, \\mathrm{e}^x) = x(x + 1)^2$ 两边对 $x$ 求导得",
        "bbox": [
            115,
            361,
            591,
            379
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nf _ {1} ^ {\\prime} (x + 1, \\mathrm {e} ^ {x}) + \\mathrm {e} ^ {x} f _ {2} ^ {\\prime} (x + 1, \\mathrm {e} ^ {x}) = (x + 1) ^ {2} + 2 x (x + 1),\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            244,
            383,
            808,
            401
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "取 $x = 0$ 得 $f_{1}^{\\prime}(1,1) + f_{2}^{\\prime}(1,1) = 1$ ",
        "bbox": [
            115,
            404,
            466,
            422
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$f(x,x^{2}) = 2x^{2}\\ln x$ 两边对 $x$ 求导得 ",
        "bbox": [
            115,
            428,
            468,
            445
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nf _ {1} ^ {\\prime} (x, x ^ {2}) + 2 x f _ {2} ^ {\\prime} (x, x ^ {2}) = 4 x \\ln x + 2 x,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            319,
            449,
            733,
            468
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "取 $x = 1$ 得 $f_{1}^{\\prime}(1,1) + 2f_{2}^{\\prime}(1,1) = 2$ ",
        "bbox": [
            115,
            472,
            476,
            489
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "解得 $f_{1}^{\\prime}(1,1) = 0, f_{2}^{\\prime}(1,1) = 1$ ，故 $\\mathrm{d}f(1,1) = \\mathrm{d}y$ ，应选(C).",
        "bbox": [
            115,
            493,
            672,
            511
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（3）【答案】 （A）.",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            515,
            250,
            532
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】因为 $f(x) = \\frac{\\sin x}{1 + x^2}$ 为奇函数，所以 $b = 0$ ",
        "bbox": [
            115,
            539,
            585,
            571
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $\\sin x = x - \\frac{x^3}{6} + o(x^3), \\frac{1}{1 + x^2} = 1 - x^2 + o(x^3)$ 得",
        "bbox": [
            117,
            579,
            644,
            613
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nf (x) = \\frac {\\sin x}{1 + x ^ {2}} = x - \\frac {7}{6} x ^ {3} + o \\left(x ^ {3}\\right),\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            349,
            621,
            701,
            655
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "应选（A）.",
        "bbox": [
            117,
            660,
            208,
            677
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（4）【答案】 （B）.",
        "bbox": [
            82,
            682,
            246,
            699
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $\\lim_{n\\to \\infty}\\sum_{k = 1}^{n}f\\left(\\frac{2k - 1}{2n}\\right)\\frac{1}{n} = \\lim_{n\\to \\infty}\\sum_{k = 1}^{n}f\\left(\\frac{2k}{2n}\\right)\\frac{1}{n} = \\lim_{n\\to \\infty}\\frac{1}{n}\\sum_{k = 1}^{n}f\\left(\\frac{k}{n}\\right) = \\int_{0}^{1}f(x)\\mathrm{d}x$ ，应选(B).（5）【答案】 (B).",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            703,
            931,
            760
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 令 $\\mathbf{A} = \\begin{pmatrix} 0 & 1 & 1\\\\ 1 & 2 & 1\\\\ 1 & 1 & 0 \\end{pmatrix} ,\\mathbf{X} = \\begin{pmatrix} x_{1}\\\\ x_{2}\\\\ x_{3} \\end{pmatrix}$ ，则 $f = X^{\\mathrm{T}}AX$ ",
        "bbox": [
            113,
            767,
            606,
            828
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $|\\lambda \\pmb {E} - \\pmb {A}| = \\left| \\begin{array}{rrr}\\lambda & -1 & -1\\\\ -1 & \\lambda -2 & -1\\\\ -1 & -1 & \\lambda \\end{array} \\right| = (\\lambda +1)\\left| \\begin{array}{rrr}1 & 0 & 0\\\\ -1 & \\lambda -2 & -2\\\\ -1 & -1 & \\lambda -1 \\end{array} \\right|$ ",
        "bbox": [
            115,
            834,
            723,
            895
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n= (\\lambda + 1) \\left(\\lambda^ {2} - 3 \\lambda\\right) = 0\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            232,
            899,
            454,
            915
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "得 $\\lambda_{1} = -1, \\lambda_{2} = 0, \\lambda_{3} = 3$ ，应选（B）.",
        "bbox": [
            115,
            920,
            452,
            938
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（6）【答案】 （A）.",
        "bbox": [
            70,
            70,
            240,
            86
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】由施密特正交化得 $l_{1} = \\frac{(\\pmb{\\alpha}_{3},\\pmb{\\beta}_{1})}{(\\pmb{\\beta}_{1},\\pmb{\\beta}_{1})} = \\frac{5}{2}, l_{2} = \\frac{(\\pmb{\\alpha}_{3},\\pmb{\\beta}_{2})}{(\\pmb{\\beta}_{2},\\pmb{\\beta}_{2})} = \\frac{2}{4} = \\frac{1}{2}$ 应选(A). ",
        "bbox": [
            103,
            91,
            846,
            130
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "方法点评：将线性无关的向量组化为两两正交的规范向量组即施密特正交规范化，实对称矩阵的对角化的正交变换法需要将线性无关的特征向量进行正交化和单位化.设 $\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1},\\pmb{\\alpha}_{2},\\pmb{\\alpha}_{3}$ 线性无关， $\\pmb {\\beta}_1 = \\pmb {\\alpha}_1,\\pmb {\\beta}_2 = \\pmb {\\alpha}_2 - l_1\\pmb {\\beta}_1,\\pmb {\\beta}_3 = \\pmb {\\alpha}_3 - k_1\\pmb {\\beta}_1 - k_2\\pmb {\\beta}_2$ ，且 $\\pmb {\\beta}_1,\\pmb {\\beta}_2,\\pmb {\\beta}_3$ 线性无关，则 $l_{1} = \\frac{(\\pmb{\\alpha}_{2},\\pmb{\\beta}_{1})}{(\\pmb{\\beta}_{1},\\pmb{\\beta}_{1})},k_{1} = \\frac{(\\pmb{\\alpha}_{3},\\pmb{\\beta}_{1})}{(\\pmb{\\beta}_{1},\\pmb{\\beta}_{1})},k_{2} = \\frac{(\\pmb{\\alpha}_{3},\\pmb{\\beta}_{2})}{(\\pmb{\\beta}_{2},\\pmb{\\beta}_{2})}.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            68,
            139,
            927,
            247
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（7）【答案】 (C).",
        "bbox": [
            70,
            257,
            238,
            273
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $r\\begin{pmatrix} \\mathbf{A} & \\mathbf{O}\\\\ \\mathbf{O} & \\mathbf{A}^{\\mathrm{T}}\\mathbf{A} \\end{pmatrix} = r(\\mathbf{A}) + r(\\mathbf{A}^{\\mathrm{T}}\\mathbf{A}) = 2r(\\mathbf{A});$ ",
        "bbox": [
            105,
            280,
            553,
            318
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $\\left( \\begin{array}{ll}A & AB\\\\ O & A^{\\mathrm{T}} \\end{array} \\right)\\xrightarrow{\\text{列}}\\left( \\begin{array}{ll}A & O\\\\ O & A^{\\mathrm{T}} \\end{array} \\right)$ 得 $r\\left( \\begin{array}{ll}A & AB\\\\ O & A^{\\mathrm{T}} \\end{array} \\right) = 2r(A)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            107,
            325,
            571,
            363
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $r\\left(\\begin{array}{cc}\\mathbf{A}&\\mathbf{O}\\\\ \\mathbf{B}\\mathbf{A}&\\mathbf{A}^{\\mathrm{T}}\\end{array}\\right)\\xrightarrow{\\text{行}}r\\left(\\begin{array}{cc}\\mathbf{A}&\\mathbf{O}\\\\ \\mathbf{O}&\\mathbf{A}^{\\mathrm{T}}\\end{array}\\right)$ 得 $r\\left(\\begin{array}{cc}\\mathbf{A}&\\mathbf{O}\\\\ \\mathbf{B}\\mathbf{A}&\\mathbf{A}^{\\mathrm{T}}\\end{array}\\right)=2r(\\mathbf{A})$ ，应选(C).",
        "bbox": [
            107,
            369,
            705,
            408
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（8）【答案】 (D).",
        "bbox": [
            70,
            415,
            240,
            432
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】由 $P(A\\mid B) = P(A)$ 得 $P(AB) = P(A)P(B)$ ，即事件 $A,B$ 独立，",
        "bbox": [
            105,
            436,
            804,
            454
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "于是 $P(A|\\overline{B}) = \\frac{P(A\\overline{B})}{P(\\overline{B})} = \\frac{P(A)P(\\overline{B})}{P(\\overline{B})} = P(A)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            107,
            458,
            569,
            502
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $P(A\\mid B) > P(A)$ 得 $P(AB) > P(A)P(B)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            107,
            507,
            577,
            525
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "从而 $P(\\overline{A}|\\overline{B}) = \\frac{P(\\overline{A}\\overline{B})}{P(\\overline{B})} = \\frac{1 - P(A) - P(B) + P(AB)}{1 - P(B)}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            109,
            529,
            644,
            573
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n> \\frac {1 - P (A) - P (B) + P (A) P (B)}{1 - P (B)} = 1 - P (A) = P (\\overline {{A}});\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            244,
            579,
            800,
            613
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $P(A|B) > P(A|\\overline{B})$ 得 $\\frac{P(AB)}{P(B)} >\\frac{P(A) - P(AB)}{1 - P(B)}$ 整理得 $P(AB) > P(A)P(B)$ 则 $P(A|B) = \\frac{P(AB)}{P(B)} >\\frac{P(A)P(B)}{P(B)} = P(A)$ ，应选(D).",
        "bbox": [
            109,
            620,
            927,
            694
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（9）【答案】 (C).",
        "bbox": [
            72,
            700,
            240,
            717
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $\\overline{X} \\sim N\\left(\\mu_1, \\frac{\\sigma_1^2}{n}\\right), \\overline{Y} \\sim N\\left(\\mu_2, \\frac{\\sigma_2^2}{n}\\right)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            107,
            721,
            498,
            757
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "则 $E(\\hat{\\theta}) = E(\\overline{X}) - E(\\overline{Y}) = \\mu_1 - \\mu_2 = \\theta$ ",
        "bbox": [
            109,
            766,
            490,
            787
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} D (\\hat {\\theta}) = D (\\bar {X} - \\bar {Y}) = D (\\bar {X}) + D (\\bar {Y}) - 2 \\operatorname {C o v} (\\bar {X}, \\bar {Y}) \\\\ = \\frac {\\sigma_ {1} ^ {2}}{n} + \\frac {\\sigma_ {2} ^ {2}}{n} - \\frac {2}{n} \\left[ \\operatorname {C o v} \\left(X _ {1}, \\bar {Y}\\right) + \\operatorname {C o v} \\left(X _ {2}, \\bar {Y}\\right) + \\dots + \\operatorname {C o v} \\left(X _ {n}, \\bar {Y}\\right) \\right] \\\\ = \\frac {\\sigma_ {1} ^ {2}}{n} + \\frac {\\sigma_ {2} ^ {2}}{n} - \\frac {2}{n ^ {2}} \\left[ \\operatorname {C o v} \\left(X _ {1}, Y _ {1}\\right) + \\operatorname {C o v} \\left(X _ {2}, Y _ {2}\\right) + \\dots + \\operatorname {C o v} \\left(X _ {n}, Y _ {n}\\right) \\right] \\\\ = \\frac {\\sigma_ {1} ^ {2}}{n} + \\frac {\\sigma_ {2} ^ {2}}{n} - \\frac {2}{n ^ {2}} \\cdot n \\rho \\sigma_ {1} \\sigma_ {2} = \\frac {\\sigma_ {1} ^ {2} + \\sigma_ {2} ^ {2} - 2 \\rho \\sigma_ {1} \\sigma_ {2}}{n}, \\text {应 选 (C)}. \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            129,
            792,
            812,
            936
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（10）【答案】 (B).",
        "bbox": [
            74,
            66,
            252,
            84
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】由题 $\\overline{X}\\sim N\\left(11.5,\\frac{1}{4}\\right)$ ，或 $\\frac{\\overline{X} - 11.5}{\\frac{1}{2}}\\sim N(0,1),$ ",
        "bbox": [
            119,
            87,
            650,
            141
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "犯第二类错误的概率为",
        "bbox": [
            121,
            147,
            339,
            164
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nP \\{\\overline {{X}} <   1 1 \\} = P \\left\\{\\frac {\\overline {{X}} - 1 1 . 5}{\\frac {1}{2}} <   - 1 \\right\\} = \\Phi (- 1) = 1 - \\Phi (1),\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            252,
            168,
            797,
            232
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "应选（B）. ",
        "bbox": [
            121,
            237,
            210,
            255
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "二、填空题",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            74,
            260,
            177,
            276
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(11)【答案】 $\\frac{\\pi}{4}$ .",
        "bbox": [
            74,
            286,
            244,
            315
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $\\int_{0}^{+\\infty}\\frac{\\mathrm{d}x}{x^2 + 2x + 2} = \\int_{0}^{+\\infty}\\frac{\\mathrm{d}(x + 1)}{1 + (x + 1)^2} = \\arctan (x + 1)\\mid_{0}^{+\\infty} = \\frac{\\pi}{2} -\\frac{\\pi}{4} = \\frac{\\pi}{4}.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            119,
            321,
            874,
            357
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(12)【答案】 $\\frac{2}{3}$ .",
        "bbox": [
            74,
            363,
            244,
            394
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $\\frac{\\mathrm{dy}}{\\mathrm{dx}} = \\frac{\\mathrm{dy} / \\mathrm{dt}}{\\mathrm{dx} / \\mathrm{dt}} = \\frac{4te^{t} + 2t}{2e^{t} + 1} = 2t, \\frac{\\mathrm{d}^2y}{\\mathrm{dx}^2} = \\frac{\\mathrm{d}(2t) / \\mathrm{dt}}{\\mathrm{dx} / \\mathrm{dt}} = \\frac{2}{2e^{t} + 1},$ ",
        "bbox": [
            119,
            401,
            715,
            438
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "则 $\\frac{\\mathrm{d}^2y}{\\mathrm{d}x^2}\\bigg|_{t = 0} = \\frac{2}{3}.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            121,
            442,
            274,
            477
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（13）【答案】 $x^{2}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            74,
            482,
            240,
            500
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 令 $x = \\mathrm{e}^{t},D = \\frac{\\mathrm{d}}{\\mathrm{d}t}$ ，则",
        "bbox": [
            119,
            504,
            385,
            538
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nx y ^ {\\prime} = D y, x ^ {2} y ^ {\\prime \\prime} = D (D - 1) y,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            375,
            543,
            670,
            561
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "代入欧拉方程得",
        "bbox": [
            119,
            564,
            274,
            582
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\frac {\\mathrm {d} ^ {2} y}{\\mathrm {d} t ^ {2}} - 4 y = 0,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            454,
            586,
            591,
            621
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "特征方程为 $\\lambda^2 - 4 = 0$ ，特征根为 $\\lambda_1 = -2, \\lambda_2 = 2$ ",
        "bbox": [
            119,
            627,
            587,
            646
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$\\frac{\\mathrm{d}^2y}{\\mathrm{d}t^2} - 4y = 0$ 的通解为 $y = C_1\\mathrm{e}^{-2t} + C_2\\mathrm{e}^{2t}$ ，原方程的通解为",
        "bbox": [
            119,
            649,
            668,
            685
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\ny = \\frac {C _ {1}}{x ^ {2}} + C _ {2} x ^ {2},\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            444,
            692,
            600,
            727
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $y(1) = 1, y'(1) = 2$ 得 $C_1 + C_2 = 1, -2C_1 + 2C_2 = 2$ ，解得 $C_1 = 0, C_2 = 1$ ，故 $y = x^2$ .",
        "bbox": [
            117,
            731,
            840,
            771
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "方法点评：形如",
        "bbox": [
            119,
            781,
            262,
            799
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
