    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{\\int_{0}^{x}\\mathrm{e}^{t^2}\\mathrm{d}t}{\\mathrm{e}^x - 1} = \\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{\\mathrm{e}^{x^2}}{\\mathrm{e}^x} = 1,$ ",
