        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\left(\\frac {1}{\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} - \\frac {1}{\\sin x}\\right) = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {\\sin x - \\mathrm {e} ^ {x} + 1}{(\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1) \\sin x} = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {\\sin x - \\mathrm {e} ^ {x} + 1}{x ^ {2}} \\\\ = \\frac {1}{2} \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {\\cos x - e ^ {x}}{x} = \\frac {1}{2} \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} (- \\sin x - e ^ {x}) = - \\frac {1}{2}, \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
