        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\left(\\frac {1 + \\int_ {0} ^ {x} \\mathrm {e} ^ {t ^ {2}} \\mathrm {d} t}{\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} - \\frac {1}{\\sin x}\\right) = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\left[ \\frac {1 + x + \\frac {x ^ {3}}{3} + o \\left(x ^ {3}\\right)}{\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} - \\frac {1}{\\sin x} \\right] = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\left(\\frac {1 + x}{\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} - \\frac {1}{\\sin x}\\right) \\\\ = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {x}{\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} + \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\left(\\frac {1}{\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - 1} - \\frac {1}{\\sin x}\\right) \\\\ = 1 + \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {\\sin x - e ^ {x} + 1}{\\left(e ^ {x} - 1\\right) \\sin x} = 1 + \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {\\sin x - e ^ {x} + 1}{x ^ {2}} \\\\ = 1 + \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {\\cos x - e ^ {x}}{2 x} = 1 + \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {- \\sin x - e ^ {x}}{2} = \\frac {1}{2}. \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
