        "text": "且 $S_{1}(x) = \\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}\\mathrm{e}^{-nx} = \\frac{\\mathrm{e}^{-x}}{1 - \\mathrm{e}^{-x}} = \\frac{1}{\\mathrm{e}^{x} - 1};$ ",
