        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} I \\left(D _ {1}\\right) = \\iint_ {D _ {1}} \\left(4 - x ^ {2} - y ^ {2}\\right) \\mathrm {d} x \\mathrm {d} y = 2 \\pi \\int_ {0} ^ {2} r \\left(4 - r ^ {2}\\right) \\mathrm {d} r \\\\ = 2 \\pi \\int_ {0} ^ {2} (4 r - r ^ {3}) \\mathrm {d} r = 2 \\pi (8 - 4) = 8 \\pi ; \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
