        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} \\int_ {\\partial D _ {1}} \\frac {(x e ^ {x ^ {2} + 4 y ^ {2}} + y) d x + (4 y e ^ {x ^ {2} + 4 y ^ {2}} - x) d y}{x ^ {2} + 4 y ^ {2}} \\\\ = \\oint_ {\\partial D _ {1} + L _ {0} ^ {-}} \\frac {(x e ^ {x ^ {2} + 4 y ^ {2}} + y) d x + (4 y e ^ {x ^ {2} + 4 y ^ {2}} - x) d y}{x ^ {2} + 4 y ^ {2}} + \\\\ \\int_ {L _ {0}} \\frac {\\left(x \\mathrm {e} ^ {x ^ {2} + 4 y ^ {2}} + y\\right) \\mathrm {d} x + \\left(4 y \\mathrm {e} ^ {x ^ {2} + 4 y ^ {2}} - x\\right) \\mathrm {d} y}{x ^ {2} + 4 y ^ {2}}, \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
